CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 14, 1945, pg. 26 reads: "The Winnahs! - Smiling victoriously over the awards they received recently in Cosmalite Club'd Baby Contest, held at Ammon Recreation Center on June 29, are Yvonne Elizabeth Jackson, first prize winner; Asa Gaines Hunter, second prize; Delilah Moten, third prize. First prize was a $25 war bond. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Yvonne Elizabeth Jackson, Asa Gaines Hunter, and Delilah Moten holding babies on top of upright piano, in Ammon Recreation Center for Cosmalite Club's Baby Contest
